# === TYPE ===
# feat     -> nuova funzionalità
# fix      -> bug fix
# docs     -> documentazione
# style    -> formatting (no logica)
# refactor -> refactoring
# test     -> test
# chore    -> manutenzione

<type>(<scope>): <short summary>

# ------------------------
# CONTEXT
# Cosa cambia e perché (NON come)
# ------------------------
<detailed explanation>

# ------------------------
# CHANGES
# Lista delle modifiche principali
# ------------------------
- ...
- ...
- ...

# ------------------------
# IMPACT
# Breaking changes / effetti collaterali
# ------------------------
- ...

# ------------------------
# REFERENCES
# Issue / ticket
# ------------------------
Closes: #
Related: #

# ------------------------
# AI NOTES (opzionale, utile per Codex)
# ------------------------
# reasoning:
# alternatives_considered:
# next_steps:




example:
feat(auth): add JWT authentication

Add JWT-based authentication system to improve security
and support stateless sessions.

- Implement login endpoint
- Add token generation
- Secure protected routes with middleware

Breaking change: session-based auth removed

Closes: #42


